data.title: Iraq – All Content on this topic – Page 36 of 73 – DW
data.meta_description: The US-led invasion of Iraq in 2003 saw the end of the 24-year-long rule of dictator Saddam Hussein. The consequences remain to this day, as Iraq is wrecked by ongoing conflict and crises.
